Black Magic - An educational tool designed to raise awareness of Black folk of significant achievement in celebration of Black History Month. Each day, the app will profile a person, their contributions to society and the impact those contributions make today.

Children in grade school can use this app in order to learn more about the impact our people had in society and also use this as a tool to educate others, whether in or out of class.

Black Magic can provide education and entertainment to the approximately 24.4 million African American kids in grade school take pride in past achievements and improve their confidence while embarking on their educational studies.